eft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"For drawing the Witch's attention..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"[chara:104700:effect_shake]Oh g-g-gosh! It's no trouble at all!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"So I guess you made it out safely after...that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Y-yeah!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I can't thank you enough for rescuing me way@back when!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I really wanted to see you again and say thanks..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I was looking all over for you!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"*Sigh* And now my dream has finally come@true!"},{"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yeah, I guess it did..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3010_vista_16_9.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_46120.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":6120,"name":"sprite_0","pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event05","nameCenter":"","textCenter":"—!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":6120,"name":"sprite_0"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20811.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"exitWitchSpace","se":"7209_gate_close","surround":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20814.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"fade"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Hoo-wee... I thought I was a goner!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Thank you so, so much."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...Mm."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"I once saved this girl by defeating a Witch.","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"But that's just how she saw it.@The truth was different."},{"narration":"Her Soul Gem was cloudy from fighting Witches,@and she asked me if I had any Grief Seeds...@But I lied and didn't share mine with her."},{"narration":"She was much weaker than I was,@and all by herself,@so she must've been anxious."},{"narration":"But back then, I was more pathetic than I am now,@and I was so stressed and overwhelmed by my own@problems that I thought, \"if you're a Magical Girl,@you should be able to take care of yourself\"."},{"narration":"This girl was even weaker than me,@and I basically left her to die..."},{"narration":"I've been trying my hardest to change, but...@The only reason I managed to do that@is because of Tamaki-san.@I doubt the real me has changed at all."},{"narration":"I couldn't get any closer to my ideal,@Tamaki-san vanished like smoke,@and on top of that, this girl showed back up..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_46403.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I never expected to run into you in a Witch's@Labyrinth, but...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I guess you could say that's par for the course for@Magical Girls, huh!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"It's pretty ironic, honestly..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Eh...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104300,"motion":100},{"id":104700,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Sorry, I was talking to myself."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Really?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"You know, even though this is just a coincidence,@it feels like fate!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"My grandma lives around here, and I happened@to be visiting her."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I may be weak, but I decided to go out and patrol@the area anyway!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...Ack, sorry! I made this all about me...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Uh... Oh, right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"We should probably focus on those Witches@for now."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":104700}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_46403.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"bgm24_story04","chara":[{"cutInId":1,"id":6403,"name":"sprite_1","pos":1,"zOrder":110.0},{"cutInId":1,"id":6403,"name":"sprite_0","pos":0,"zOrder":100.0},{"cutInId":1,"id":6403,"name":"sprite_2","pos":2,"zOrder":120.0}],"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"chara":[{"cutInId":1,"effect":"fadeout","id":6403,"name":"sprite_1"},{"cutInId":1,"effect":"fadeout","id":6403,"name":"sprite_0"},{"cutInId":1,"effect":"fadeout","id":6403,"name":"sprite_2"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_46403.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"[chara:104700:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]W-wha?! They're still there?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"They look like they're preparing to make their@move..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I c-c-can't stay scared forever!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I've been training hard after school every day..."},{"chara":[{"id":104700}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...to try to get closer to you!"},{"chara":[{"id":104700,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Both of you, please sit back and watch me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Ah...sure..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nagisa","textRight":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200701},{"effect":"fadeout","id":104300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104700,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[flashEffect:explosion]ORYAAAAAAAH!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"}]},"version":3}
